      "wickermandef": "The model gains Flammable, Flaming Attacks, and Grind Attacks (3D3). These Grind Attacks are resolved with Strength 4, AP 0, and Flaming Attacks.",
      "redhaze": "Red Haze",
      "redhazedef": "Boosts Strength and AP, but risks harming the bearer.",
      "darkconclave": "Dark Conclave",
      "darkconclavedef": "Spells cast by this unit gains +12 Range. At list building, choose a Character from the Daemon Legions Army Book and note it on your Army List. During your Magic Phase in Game Turn 4, 5, or 6, instead of performing a Daemonic Summon with this model, you may replace it with the selected Character. The Character may take a mount option, but cannot take any upgrades or other optional selections. It also loses all magic levels and spells.",
